Name: Denoteone
AboutMe:
Interactive Media Developer.

"The prince of Web 2.0", "The guru of Web usability", and "The diva of design and development" are just a few names that Mike tries, unsuccessfully, to get his teammates to call him. Mike's core background centers on Web application development in PHP, PERL, MySQL and other fancy web languages. After majoring in graphic design at Columbia College of Chicago, Mike gravitated toward Flash application design and development which began a lifelong love of Web design & development. With 10 years of industry experience and the support of his amazing family, Mike strives to provide clients with the most cutting-edge web applications.
